                "PRETORIA BURSARY PROGRAMME 2024 (MBSA)\nJob category: Personal\nDepartment: HR MB South Africa M&S & HR Services Pretoria\nOrganization: Mercedes-Benz South Africa Ltd\nLocation: Pretoria, ZA\nStart date: Immediately\nPublication date: 02.11.2023\nJob number: MER0002WPM\n \nTasks\nGet a head start into the world of work by participating in the Mercedes-Benz South Africa Bursary Programme, and transport your career with one of the world\u2019s most successful automotive companies. The Programme aims to harness outstanding achievers at Grade 12 and Tertiary levels into our fold of growing Talent, by offering the participant financial aid for studies as well as experiential learning. \n \nWhy a Mercedes-Benz South Africa Bursary? \nStudy at a University of your choice*\nTuition fees, accommodation/transport expenses, stipend, textbooks and digital allowances are paid for*\nWork at Mercedes-Benz, Pretoria (Menlyn Maine) during your school vacations*\nJoin the MBSA Graduate Development programme after studying*\n*Conditions apply\n \n \nWho can apply?\n \nQualifications\nWhat is the selection criteria?\nGrade 12 with at least 65% average for your final matric results\n65% average at tertiary level for the most recent semester results\n \n \nContact\nMercedes-Benz South Africa Ltd\nMBSA Place, 210 Aramist Place\n0181 Pretoria\nKayleigh Anne Pretorius\nE-Mail: kayleigh_anne.pretorius@mercedes-benz.com\n \nJOIN US"
