                " \n \n \n \nINTERNSHIP PROGRAMME @ FAMOUS BRANDS FOR PEOPLE LIVING WITH DISABILITIES AT FAMOUS BRANDS\nFAMOUS BRANDS\nUndisclosed\nInternship position\nMpumalanga\nJob 2540197\n \nAPPLY NOW\n \nABOUT THE POSITION\nFamous Brands is excited to run another PWD Internship Programme. As you know, internships are linked to fields of study and occupations, so send your CV to us, and we'll see which role best suits your qualifications.\nThe interns that will be considered are youth living with disabilities between the ages of 18 and 34 years who have not yet entered employment or who are currently unemployed.\nApplicants for internship opportunities must be South African citizens based in Gauteng, Mpumalanga, Free State, KZN, Western Cape & Eastern Cape. This will be a 12-month internship programme starting from the 01st of November 2023.\nApplied after the 1st of November? No problem! Your application will be kept in our database, and should there still be availability, your application will be considered.\n \nIn Summary, our selection criteria are:\nPeople Living with Disabilities (with Note of diagnosis)\nSouth African citizen\nBetween the ages of 18 and 34\nTertiary Qualification\nIndividual that has never been on a YES programme before.\n \nDesired Skills:\nPunctuality\nMotivated\n \nAPPLY NOW\n \n \n \n \n ",
